briefdescription.para: Process a disable background checking for the Eeprom table command.

simplesect.title: Description
simplesect.para: Disables background checking for the Eeprom table

simplesect.title: Assumptions, External Events, and Notes:
simplesect.para: In order for background checking of individual areas to checksum (OS code segment, cFE core, Eeprom, Memory, Apps, and Tables) to occur, the table must be enabled and overall checksumming must be enabled.

parameterdescription.para: A CFE_SB_MsgPtr_t pointer that references the software bus message

briefdescription.para: Process an enable background checking for an Eeprom entry command.

simplesect.title: Description
simplesect.para: Allows the specified Eeprom entry to be background checksummed.

simplesect.title: Assumptions, External Events, and Notes:
simplesect.para: In order for background checking of individual entries to checksum to occur, the entry must be enabled, the table must be enabled and, overall checksumming must be enabled. This command updates both the results table and the definition table. If the entry exists in the results table but not in the definition table, the command is still successful, but the definition table is not updated. If the entry does not exist in the results table, neither table is updated.

parameterdescription.para: A CFE_SB_MsgPtr_t pointer that references the software bus message
